scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Pages 700-733, with typed fragments on reverse of p. 709, 720, 728 and 732; fragment on reverse of p. 720 indicates that this is written post-1983; two alternates of p. 731, corresponds to p. 695-729 of Typescript Version; p. 739-740, with typed fragment on reverse of p. 740, corresponds to p. 732-735 in Typescript Version. Heavily edited, with cut-and-paste sections.
